This Spotify Clone is built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It mimics the popular music streaming platform’s interface and core functionalities, including play, pause, next, and previous controls. The responsive design adapts to different devices, while JavaScript adds interactivity, creating a smooth and user-friendly music streaming experience.
